# 🎓 GATE 2027 Progress Tracker

A full-stack GATE CSE preparation platform built with **React + Node.js + MongoDB Atlas + JWT Auth**.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
gate2027/
├── frontend/                  # React.js (Vite + Tailwind CSS)
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   ├── auth/          # Login, Register, ForgotPassword
│   │   │   ├── dashboard/     # Stats, Countdown, WeekChart
│   │   │   ├── subjects/      # SubjectCard, TopicList
│   │   │   ├── topics/        # TopicTracker, AddTopicModal
│   │   │   ├── pyq/           # PYQCard, PYQFilter
│   │   │   ├── mocks/         # MockTestTable, ScoreChart
│   │   │   ├── analytics/     # RadarChart, StreakGrid, WeakTopics
│   │   │   ├── notes/         # NoteCard, NoteEditor
│   │   │   ├── admin/         # AdminPanel, SubjectManager
│   │   │   └── common/        # Navbar, Sidebar, Modal, Button
│   │   ├── pages/             # Page-level components
│   │   ├── context/           # AuthContext, ThemeContext
│   │   ├── hooks/             # useAuth, useProgress, useSubjects
│   │   ├── services/          # API service functions
│   │   ├── utils/             # helpers, validators
│   │   └── styles/            # Tailwind config, globals
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── vite.config.js
│   ├── tailwind.config.js
│   └── package.json
│
├── backend/                   # Node.js + Express.js
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── controllers/       # Auth, Subject, Topic, Note, Mock, PYQ
│   │   ├── models/            # MongoDB Mongoose schemas
│   │   ├── middleware/        # auth, error, validate, rateLimit
│   │   ├── routes/            # API route definitions
│   │   ├── config/            # DB connection, env config
│   │   └── utils/             # email, jwt, helpers
│   ├── tests/                 # Jest unit tests
│   ├── server.js
│   └── package.json
│
├── .github/
│   └── workflows/             # CI/CD pipelines
├── .env.example
└── README.md
```

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18 + Vite + Tailwind CSS |
| Backend | Node.js 20 + Express.js 4 |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas (Mongoose ODM) |
| Auth | JWT (Access + Refresh tokens) |
| Charts | Chart.js 4 |
| Deploy FE | Vercel |
| Deploy BE | Render.com |
| Email | Nodemailer + SendGrid |

---

## ⚡ Quick Start

### 1. Clone & Install

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourname/gate2027.git
cd gate2027

# Install backend
cd backend && npm install

# Install frontend
cd ../frontend && npm install
```

### 2. Configure Environment

```bash
# Backend .env
cp .env.example backend/.env
# Fill in MongoDB URI, JWT secret, etc.

# Frontend .env
cp .env.example frontend/.env
# Set VITE_API_URL
```

### 3. Run Development

```bash
# Terminal 1 – Backend (port 5000)
cd backend && npm run dev

# Terminal 2 – Frontend (port 5173)
cd frontend && npm run dev
```

---

## 🌐 Deployment

### Frontend → Vercel
```bash
cd frontend
npm run build
# Connect repo to Vercel, set VITE_API_URL env var
vercel --prod
```

### Backend → Render
1. Create new **Web Service** on Render
2. Connect GitHub repo → select `/backend`
3. Build: `npm install` | Start: `npm start`
4. Set all environment variables in Render dashboard
5. Use Render's free MongoDB add-on or MongoDB Atlas

---

## 📡 REST API Documentation

### Auth Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | /api/auth/register | Register new user |
| POST | /api/auth/login | Login, returns JWT |
| POST | /api/auth/refresh | Refresh access token |
| POST | /api/auth/forgot-password | Send reset email |
| POST | /api/auth/reset-password | Reset with token |
| GET | /api/auth/me | Get current user |
| PUT | /api/auth/profile | Update profile |

### Subject Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | /api/subjects | Get all subjects |
| GET | /api/subjects/:id | Get subject + topics |
| POST | /api/subjects | Create subject (admin) |
| PUT | /api/subjects/:id | Update subject (admin) |
| DELETE | /api/subjects/:id | Delete subject (admin) |

### Topic Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | /api/topics | Get all topics |
| GET | /api/topics?subject=:id | Filter by subject |
| POST | /api/topics | Add topic |
| PUT | /api/topics/:id | Edit topic |
| PATCH | /api/topics/:id/toggle | Toggle complete |
| DELETE | /api/topics/:id | Delete topic |

### Progress Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | /api/progress | Overall progress stats |
| GET | /api/progress/subject/:id | Subject progress |
| PUT | /api/progress/study-hours | Log study hours |
| GET | /api/progress/streak | Get study streak |

### Mock Test Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | /api/mocks | Get all mock tests |
| POST | /api/mocks | Add mock test |
| PUT | /api/mocks/:id | Edit mock test |
| DELETE | /api/mocks/:id | Delete mock test |
| GET | /api/mocks/analytics | Score trend data |

### PYQ Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | /api/pyq | Get all PYQs |
| GET | /api/pyq?subject=&year=&difficulty= | Filtered PYQs |
| PATCH | /api/pyq/:id/solved | Toggle solved |
| POST | /api/pyq | Add PYQ (admin) |

### Notes Endpoints
| Method | Route | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | /api/notes | Get all notes |
| POST | /api/notes | Create note |
| PUT | /api/notes/:id | Update note |
| DELETE | /api/notes/:id | Delete note |

---

## 🗄️ MongoDB Schema Design

See `backend/src/models/` for all Mongoose schemas.

### ER Relationships
```
User ──< Progress (1:1)
User ──< Notes (1:N)
User ──< MockTests (1:N)
User ──< UserTopicProgress (1:N)
Subject ──< Topics (1:N)
Topic ──< PYQ (1:N)
```

